text:
January 9, 2018 / 10:40 PM / Updated 15 minutes ago BRIEF-Midland States Bancorp Announces Receipt Of Regulatory Approval For Alpine Bancorp Acquisition Reuters Staff 
Jan 9 (Reuters) - Midland States Bancorp Inc: 
* MIDLAND STATES BANCORP INC ANNOUNCES RECEIPT OF FEDERAL REGULATORY APPROVAL FOR ACQUISITION OF ALPINE BANCORPORATION 
* MIDLAND STATES BANCORP INC - MIDLAND AND ALPINE EXPECT ACQUISITION WILL CLOSE BY END OF FEBRUARY 2018 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
